---
layout: base
title: "TopClanker - AI Agent Rankings"
description: "No-bullshit rankings of AI agents. Find the best reasoning, math, research, and learning models."
permalink: /index.html
---

<!-- Hero -->
<section class="bg-gradient-to-r from-blue-600 to-purple-600 text-white py-16">
    <div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8 text-center">
        <h2 class="text-4xl md:text-5xl font-bold mb-4">AI Agent Rankings</h2>
        <p class="text-xl md:text-2xl mb-2 text-blue-100">Ranked by published benchmarks. No bullshit.</p>
        <p class="text-lg text-blue-100 max-w-2xl mx-auto">
            We aggregate scores from peer-reviewed research: MMLU, GSM8K, HumanEval, and more.
            <a href="/methodology.html" class="underline font-medium hover:text-white">See our methodology →</a>
        </p>
    </div>
</section>

<!-- Ad Spot - Top Banner -->
<div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8 my-8">
    <div class="flex justify-center">
        <ins class="adsbygoogle"
             style="display:block"
             data-ad-client="ca-pub-7245948824993108"
             data-ad-slot="2996630786"
             data-ad-format="auto"
             data-full-width-responsive="true"></ins>
        <script>
             (adsbygoogle = window.adsbygoogle || []).push({});
        </script>
    </div>
</div>

<!-- Main Content -->
<main class="max-w-7xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8 py-8">

    <!-- Rankings Section -->
    <section id="rankings" class="mb-12">
        <div class="flex justify-between items-center mb-6">
            <h3 class="text-3xl font-bold">Top AI Agents</h3>
            <div class="text-sm text-gray-500">
                Last updated: <span id="lastUpdated">Loading...</span>
            </div>
        </div>

        <!-- Category Filter -->
        <div class="flex flex-wrap gap-2 mb-6" id="categoryFilter">
            <button class="filter-btn active" data-category="all">All</button>
            <button class="filter-btn" data-category="reasoning">Reasoning</button>
            <button class="filter-btn" data-category="math">Math</button>
            <button class="filter-btn" data-category="research">Research</button>
            <button class="filter-btn" data-category="learning">Learning</button>
        </div>

        <!-- Local Models Filter -->
        <div class="flex flex-wrap gap-2 mb-6" id="localFilter">
            <button class="filter-btn active" data-local="all">All Models</button>
            <button class="filter-btn" data-local="local">🏠 Local Only</button>
        </div>

        <!-- Memory Filter -->
        <div class="flex flex-wrap items-center gap-2 mb-6" id="memoryFilter">
            <span class="text-sm text-gray-600 font-medium">VRAM:</span>
            <select id="vramSelect" class="filter-select">
                <option value="all">All Models</option>
                <option value="8gb">8GB</option>
                <option value="12gb">12GB</option>
                <option value="16gb">16GB</option>
                <option value="24gb" selected>24GB</option>
                <option value="32gb">32GB+</option>
                <option value="api">API Only (Cloud)</option>
            </select>
            <span class="text-sm text-gray-600 font-medium ml-4">Apple:</span>
            <select id="appleSelect" class="filter-select">
                <option value="all">All</option>
                <option value="8gb">8GB Unified</option>
                <option value="16gb">16GB Unified</option>
                <option value="24gb">24GB Unified</option>
                <option value="32gb">32GB+ Unified</option>
            </select>
        </div>

        <!-- Rankings Table (Desktop) -->
        <div class="bg-white rounded-lg shadow overflow-hidden hidden md:block">
            <div class="overflow-x-auto">
                <table class="min-w-full divide-y divide-gray-200">
                    <thead class="bg-gray-50">
                        <tr>
                            <th class="px-6 py-3 text-left text-xs font-medium text-gray-500 uppercase tracking-wider">Rank</th>
                            <th class="px-6 py-3 text-left text-xs font-medium text-gray-500 uppercase tracking-wider">Agent</th>
                            <th class="px-6 py-3 text-left text-xs font-medium text-gray-500 uppercase tracking-wider">Category</th>
                            <th class="px-6 py-3 text-left text-xs font-medium text-gray-500 uppercase tracking-wider">Type</th>
                            <th class="px-6 py-3 text-left text-xs font-medium text-gray-500 uppercase tracking-wider">Privacy</th>
                            <th class="px-6 py-3 text-left text-xs font-medium text-gray-500 uppercase tracking-wider">Score</th>
                            <th class="px-6 py-3 text-left text-xs font-medium text-gray-500 uppercase tracking-wider">Link</th>
                        </tr>
                    </thead>
                    <tbody id="rankingsTableBody" class="bg-white divide-y divide-gray-200">
                        <!-- Populated by JavaScript -->
                    </tbody>
                </table>
            </div>
        </div>

        <!-- Rankings Cards (Mobile) -->
        <div id="rankingsCards" class="md:hidden space-y-4">
            <div class="bg-white rounded-lg shadow p-4 border-l-4 border-blue-500">
                <div class="flex items-start justify-between mb-2">
                    <div class="flex items-center gap-2">
                        <span class="text-lg font-bold text-gray-400">#1</span>
                        <span class="font-bold text-gray-900">Claude Opus 4.6</span>
                    </div>
                    <a href="https://claude.ai" target="_blank" rel="noopener" class="text-blue-600 hover:text-blue-800 text-sm font-medium">Visit</a>
                </div>
                <p class="text-sm text-gray-600 mb-3">The best overall. Agentic coding, 1M token context, adaptive thinking.</p>
                <div class="flex flex-wrap gap-2 mb-3">
                    <span class="text-xs px-2 py-1 rounded bg-blue-100 text-blue-700">REASONING</span>
                    <span class="text-xs px-2 py-1 rounded bg-purple-100 text-purple-700">CLOSED</span>
                </div>
                <div class="flex flex-wrap gap-1 mt-2">
                    <span class="text-xs bg-gray-100 px-2 py-1 rounded">SWE: 72%</span>
                    <span class="text-xs bg-gray-100 px-2 py-1 rounded">MMLU: 89%</span>
                    <span class="text-xs bg-gray-100 px-2 py-1 rounded">HE: 92%</span>
                    <span class="text-xs bg-gray-100 px-2 py-1 rounded">GSM: 96.4%</span>
                </div>
                <div class="flex items-center justify-between pt-3 mt-3 border-t border-gray-100">
                    <span class="text-sm text-gray-500">Privacy: HIGH</span>
                    <span class="text-2xl font-bold text-blue-600">100</span>
                </div>
            </div>

            <div class="bg-white rounded-lg shadow p-4 border-l-4 border-blue-500">
                <div class="flex items-start justify-between mb-2">
                    <div class="flex items-center gap-2">
                        <span class="text-lg font-bold text-gray-400">#2</span>
                        <span class="font-bold text-gray-900">GPT-4.5</span>
                    </div>
                    <a href="https://openai.com" target="_blank" rel="noopener" class="text-blue-600 hover:text-blue-800 text-sm font-medium">Visit</a>
                </div>
                <p class="text-sm text-gray-600 mb-3">Latest GPT-4 iteration. Strong across all benchmarks.</p>
                <div class="flex flex-wrap gap-2 mb-3">
                    <span class="text-xs px-2 py-1 rounded bg-blue-100 text-blue-700">REASONING</span>
                    <span class="text-xs px-2 py-1 rounded bg-purple-100 text-purple-700">CLOSED</span>
                </div>
                <div class="flex flex-wrap gap-1 mt-2">
                    <span class="text-xs bg-gray-100 px-2 py-1 rounded">MMLU: 88.7%</span>
                    <span class="text-xs bg-gray-100 px-2 py-1 rounded">HE: 90%</span>
                    <span class="text-xs bg-gray-100 px-2 py-1 rounded">GSM: 92%</span>
                </div>
                <div class="flex items-center justify-between pt-3 mt-3 border-t border-gray-100">
                    <span class="text-sm text-gray-500">Privacy: MEDIUM</span>
                    <span class="text-2xl font-bold text-blue-600">98</span>
                </div>
            </div>

            <p class="text-center text-gray-500 text-sm py-4">+more on desktop</p>
        </div>

        <!-- Pagination -->
        <div id="pagination" class="p-4 bg-gray-50 rounded-b-lg"></div>
    </section>

    <!-- Recent Blog Posts Section -->
    <section id="recent-blog" class="mb-12">
        <h3 class="text-3xl font-bold mb-6">Recent Blog Posts</h3>
        <div class="grid md:grid-cols-2 lg:grid-cols-3 gap-6">
            {% set recentPosts = collections.posts | reverse | slice(0, 3) %}
            {% for post in recentPosts %}
            <article class="bg-white rounded-lg shadow p-6 hover:shadow-lg transition-shadow">
                <p class="text-sm text-gray-500 mb-2">{{ post.date | dateDisplay }}</p>
                <h4 class="text-xl font-bold mb-2">
                    <a href="{{ post.url }}" class="text-gray-900 hover:text-blue-600">
                        {{ post.data.title | truncate(55) }}
                    </a>
                </h4>
                <a href="{{ post.url }}" class="text-blue-600 hover:underline text-sm font-medium">
                    Read more →
                </a>
            </article>
            {% endfor %}
        </div>
        <div class="text-center mt-6">
            <a href="/blog/" class="text-blue-600 hover:text-blue-800 font-medium">View all posts →</a>
        </div>
    </section>

    <!-- Categories Section -->
    <section id="categories" class="mb-12">
        <h3 class="text-3xl font-bold mb-6">Categories Explained</h3>
        <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 lg:grid-cols-4 gap-6">
            <div class="bg-white rounded-lg shadow p-6">
                <div class="flex items-center mb-3">
                    <span class="category-badge reasoning mr-2">Reasoning</span>
                </div>
                <p class="text-gray-600">Logic, problem-solving, and complex decision-making capabilities.</p>
            </div>
            <div class="bg-white rounded-lg shadow p-6">
                <div class="flex items-center mb-3">
                    <span class="category-badge math mr-2">Math</span>
                </div>
                <p class="text-gray-600">Mathematical computation, symbolic manipulation, and quantitative analysis.</p>
            </div>
            <div class="bg-white rounded-lg shadow p-6">
                <div class="flex items-center mb-3">
                    <span class="category-badge research mr-2">Research</span>
                </div>
                <p class="text-gray-600">Information synthesis, citation accuracy, and comprehensive analysis.</p>
            </div>
            <div class="bg-white rounded-lg shadow p-6">
                <div class="flex items-center mb-3">
                    <span class="category-badge learning mr-2">Learning</span>
                </div>
                <p class="text-gray-600">Adaptive behavior, continuous improvement, and knowledge retention.</p>
            </div>
        </div>
    </section>

    <!-- Learn Section -->
    <section id="learn" class="mb-12">
        <h3 class="text-3xl font-bold mb-6">Building Top-Tier AI Agents</h3>
        <div class="bg-white rounded-lg shadow p-8">
            <p class="text-lg text-gray-700 mb-4">
                What makes an AI agent rank well? It's not magic - it's engineering.
            </p>
            <div class="space-y-4 text-gray-600">
                <div>
                    <h4 class="font-semibold text-gray-900 mb-2">1. Clear Objectives</h4>
                    <p>Top agents have well-defined goals and success metrics. Vague objectives produce vague results.</p>
                </div>
                <div>
                    <h4 class="font-semibold text-gray-900 mb-2">2. Robust Context Handling</h4>
                    <p>The best agents maintain state, understand context windows, and know when they need more information.</p>
                </div>
                <div>
                    <h4 class="font-semibold text-gray-900 mb-2">3. Error Recovery</h4>
                    <p>Shit breaks. Top agents gracefully handle failures and provide useful feedback when things go wrong.</p>
                </div>
                <div>
                    <h4 class="font-semibold text-gray-900 mb-2">4. Privacy &amp; Data Handling</h4>
                    <p>Responsible data practices aren't optional. Clear policies on what's stored, how, and for how long.</p>
                </div>
            </div>
            <div class="mt-6">
                <a href="/blog/" class="text-blue-600 hover:text-blue-800 font-medium">Read more in our blog →</a>
            </div>
        </div>
    </section>

</main>

<script src="/app.js"></script>
